title: Frequently Asked Questions
description: Here are the frequently asked questions we receive. If you have a question that is not answered here, please contact us.

services.question: What services do you offer?
services.answer: We offer a wide range of digital services including web development, mobile app development, and digital marketing solutions.

support.question: How can I contact support?
support.answer: You can reach our support team through our contact form, by email at support@edo-studio.com, or by phone during business hours.
